      • getRequestedSaveMode

        public SaveMode getRequestedSaveMode()
        Return save mode for validation purposes. If this value is null then validators can assume that they validate activity for submission (non-draft) with possibility to downgrade with draft save. However if returned value is specified then validators must honor this setting and return appropriate errors.
        Returns:
        requested SaveMode or null
